timelineItems.desc: One of the initial rivalries in Major League Soccer is renewed when a key clash in the Eastern Conference takes center stage as D.C. United and Columbus Crew SC meet on Saturday evening at RFK Stadium.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: D.C. United vs. Columbus Crew SC | May 2, 2015

timelineItems.name: D.C. United
timelineItems.text: 9', DeLeon volley just over the bar! Great combo with Pontius off the Fabi cross. #DCU #CrewSC #DCvCLB

timelineItems.name: Chris Webb
timelineItems.text: After early domination by Columbus, it's DeLeon who goes narrowly over the bar #dcu #unitedmania

timelineItems.name: Sean Maslin
timelineItems.text: De Leon good chance there but could not capitalize #DCvCLB

timelineItems.name: Alec F. Rivera
timelineItems.text: I'm curious if Pontius will ever truly be his 2012 self ever again. #DCUvCLB #DCU #MLS

timelineItems.name: Adam Jardy
timelineItems.text: Kei Kamara has expressed some frustration on a pair of services that never reached him. #CrewSC

timelineItems.title: GOAL: Fabián Espíndola capitalizes on a Chris Rolfe break

timelineItems.name: Thomas Floyd
timelineItems.text: Rolfe to Espindola. These guys get each other. #DCU

timelineItems.name: Alicia Rodriguez

timelineItems.title: SAVE: Steve Clark quick to stop a dangerous Fabian Espindola from close range

timelineItems.name: Thomas Floyd
timelineItems.text: Fabian Espindola is now #DCU's leading scorer in all competitions this year with three goals, despite being suspended for 6 of the 10 games.

timelineItems.name: Alec F. Rivera
timelineItems.text: The biggest question for #DCU is whether Espindola can prove as disruptive to #Crew 96 as he was against #VAN. #DCUvCLB #MLS

timelineItems.text: 3- Charlie Davies scored 3 goals in the last 3 games btw NE and NYRB (inc playoffs), including 2 to seal the playoff win last season. Thorn.

timelineItems.text: #DCU now unbeaten in 16 at RFK. They didn't play great, but #CrewSC were much, much worse.

timelineItems.name: Inside MLS
timelineItems.text: FT DC 2-0: Espindola the chief architect as United survives dodgy start to ease past Crew SC. United now unbeaten in six. #DCvCLB #MLS
